00:46:50,501 --> 00:46:53,293
You know you can
tell me things, right?

1036
00:46:53,453 --> 00:46:55,278
What do you mean?

1037
00:46:55,339 --> 00:46:58,614
I just feel like I'm
always telling you all

1038
00:46:58,676 --> 00:47:01,968
my problems with Doo
and you never...

1039
00:47:02,129 --> 00:47:06,047
I don't know I just...

1040
00:47:06,141 --> 00:47:09,050
I just don't want you thinkin'
you can't tell me things.

