00:47:33,001 --> 00:47:36,728
Your gonna want one of
them lavender sachets.

1049
00:47:36,755 --> 00:47:38,413
What for?

1050
00:47:38,507 --> 00:47:40,990
Matter of fact, I think
I got one inside.

1051
00:47:41,051 --> 00:47:41,916
What?

1052
00:47:42,010 --> 00:47:43,068
[SCREAMS]

1053
00:47:43,095 --> 00:47:50,350
[LAUGHTER]

1054
00:47:50,510 --> 00:47:53,603
Why don't I just look
for it tomorrow.

1055
00:47:58,944 --> 00:48:01,194
What am I gonna
do with out you?

1056
00:48:01,354 --> 00:48:04,105
Who said anything about
doing without, little girl?

1057
00:48:04,199 --> 00:48:08,426
It's going to be me and
you together forever.

1058
00:48:08,454 --> 00:48:10,945
Three hundred dates a year.

1059
00:48:11,039 --> 00:48:14,266
You're the one with
the imagination.

1060
00:48:14,293 --> 00:48:17,452
Hey you need to get
something off your chest,

1061
00:48:17,546 --> 00:48:19,271
you just picture me
sitting right next to you.

1062
00:48:19,298 --> 00:48:25,093
I'll be there.

1063
00:48:25,804 --> 00:48:28,371
[LAUGHTER]

