he had no right interferin'.

1072
00:48:52,331 --> 00:48:53,563
But he wouldn't listen.

1073
00:48:53,624 --> 00:48:54,973
I didn't mean to hurt him,

1074
00:48:55,000 --> 00:48:56,808
just knock some sense
into him, like you said.

1075
00:48:56,835 --> 00:49:00,328
But I guess that phone was
heavier than it seemed 'cause

1076
00:49:00,422 --> 00:49:02,756
I knocked his two
front teeth out.

1077
00:49:02,916 --> 00:49:04,833
He's fine, and I
got enough money

1078
00:49:04,927 --> 00:49:06,835
