Yes Mama.

1091
00:49:37,125 --> 00:49:37,773
Welcome home baby.

1092
00:49:37,835 --> 00:49:39,292
Hey honey.

1093
00:49:40,120 --> 00:49:41,035
Well hey Charlie!

1094
00:49:41,129 --> 00:49:43,964
Is that Pasty's new car?
