1099
00:49:51,056 --> 00:49:52,547
We'll only be a couple hours,
don't you want to unpack?

1100
00:49:52,641 --> 00:49:54,048
Why would I wanna unpack for,

1101
00:49:54,142 --> 00:49:55,550
I'm leavin'
again next week.

1102
00:49:55,644 --> 00:49:56,885
Go in and lay down and relax
you must be exhausted.

1103
00:49:56,979 --> 00:50:01,723
You're not even going
to take my bags inside?

1104
00:50:01,817 --> 00:50:03,817
Tell your mama
you love her kids.

1105
00:50:03,977 --> 00:50:05,485
