1108
00:50:10,817 --> 00:50:12,717
Surprise!

1109
00:50:12,744 --> 00:50:13,718
Where'd those come from?

1110
00:50:13,745 --> 00:50:15,387
You like 'em?

1111
00:50:15,414 --> 00:50:17,831
