00:50:31,338 --> 00:50:32,253
[BELCH]

1118
00:50:32,347 --> 00:50:33,829
[LAUGHTER]

1119
00:50:33,891 --> 00:50:36,408
Either way, that was some
good cooking, ladies.

1120
00:50:36,435 --> 00:50:37,425
Looks good on ya too.

1121
00:50:37,519 --> 00:50:40,578
Well damn.

