lightnin' bugs later.

1127
00:50:50,449 --> 00:50:54,350
Thank you, sugar.

1128
00:50:54,411 --> 00:50:55,851
Hey you want another one?

1129
00:50:55,913 --> 00:50:57,037
Nah, I'm good.

1130
00:50:57,197 --> 00:51:03,785
Alright.

1131
00:51:03,879 --> 00:51:04,786
Now that the kids
are out of earshot,

1132
00:51:04,880 --> 00:51:05,954
